                            <comment id="17044294" author="emmenlau" created="Tue, 25 Feb 2020 09:51:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jensg&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jensg&quot;&gt;jensg&lt;/a&gt;&#160;you are correct that this is now broken, and I could not find a solution easily.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Failed to notify project evaluation listener.&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
{{ &amp;gt; Removing tasks from the task container is not supported. Disable the tasks or use replace() instead.}}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The actual error message seems to be related to removing tasks from a task container. But I could not find any of the deprecated methods in use in the AS3 library. So the issue is a mystery.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will make a merge request with this change reverted.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17044927" author="emmenlau" created="Tue, 25 Feb 2020 21:53:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The merge request &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/2031&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/2031&lt;/a&gt;&#160;fixes this issue by downgrading gradle consistently to the latest 5.x release. Please review and merge.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
